snippet.title: Virtual Silence Full Playthrough (*Epilepsy warning)
snippet.description:
*Contains flashing images which may not be suitable for those with photosensitive epilepsy

Idea, Programming, and Graphics by Tuukka Virtanen
Music by Erkka Virtanen

Released June 25, 2008 for Windows
Made with GameMaker
